Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:24.27,Narrator,Kai Harada,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's Morioh Radio! \NUp next, we have a letter from a "Troubled Lonesome Boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.98,Narrator,Kai Harada,0,0,0,,"Kai, I gotta tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.61,Narrator,Kai Harada,0,0,0,,I can't get a hold of my girlfriend, and it's got me feeling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:33.57,Narrator,Kai Harada,0,0,0,,You think my sudden proposal upset her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.49,Narrator,Kai Harada,0,0,0,,I already spent my entire paycheck on\N a ruby engagement ring, which is her birthstone..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm glad we finally found the bow and arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was at Otoishi Akira's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.50,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He was using his Stand to commit theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.71,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Stole five hundred million yen in goods in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The police are still investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.43,Flashback,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try using your Stand against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.93,Flashback,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'll find and kill you no matter where you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.68,Flashback,Otoishi,0,0,0,,I'm fine with prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Chili Pepper's in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even if he gets out, he won't try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.49,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro, what will you do with the bow and arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.32,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm handing it over to the Speedwagon Foundation for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's an important piece of evidence in \Nuncovering the mystery behind Stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.75,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.21,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That means this is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It was a bit anti-climactic, but yay! We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:38.88,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm still questioning Otoishi about the Stand users created from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.09,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.64,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.64,Secondary,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Japanese coffee really hits the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.14,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Ms. waitress, may I have a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Whoa! Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Be careful! I can't take my eyes off you for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.70,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke, don't you have to go? The bus will be here soon.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Well... Yeah... {These are basically just grunts, so I don't think they really need translating, lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:10.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're right. Come on, let's go. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.26,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Will those two be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.09,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:24.55,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Whoa, this cake's fuckin' delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.51,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Waitress, gimme more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.40,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Hello, Higashikata resid{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.11,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom! It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:43.20,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke? You're the last person I expected to be calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.95,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:50.54,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Well, uh... \NYou're gonna be staying at home for the rest of the day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.33,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Yeah. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.84,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,N-No reason! Just wanted to be sure! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.92,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Oh, he{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.63,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.92,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,He better not be planning something weird again... {Did this ever happen before? Should the "again" be here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:07.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Man, I hope Mom didn't think that sounded weird... {maybe change either this weird or the weird in the last line?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:14.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I told him to wait until I was off the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hello? Can you hear me? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.04,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Were you trying to call me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:37.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's no way we'll get a taxi this late, \Nso we're gonna take the bus to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:42.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,, And... Listen, I know I'm being pushy, \Nbut I wanna make sure we're on the same page here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.01,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can only look from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.81,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't even think about talking to my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I need you to promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.31,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My mom won't be happy if you show up out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,She'd be a total wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:05.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Don't need to tell me twice. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.28,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Also, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.37,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call you "Mr. Joestar."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:18.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,W-Well... Guess I should be straight with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This may seem cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:28.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but I can't call a guy I just met "Dad" or "Pops" or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,After you see my mom, \NI want you to go right back to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.02,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.82,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,That's fine with me. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.90,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Man, this is so awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:51.58,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I know being honest is best, \Nbut maybe some things are better left unsaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did you see where \Nthat buff old guy standing here just went?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.38,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,He just got on that long-distance bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:14.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You've gotta be kidding me, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.27,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You said we were getting on a bus, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.90,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you caught up to it on foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:25.28,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We nearly made it onto the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:31.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm starting to think I should have just let you ride all the way to Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.99,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Ugh, my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.54,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.88,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It feels like something is tugging at my trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Whatever you do, don't let it drag you off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.47,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,J-Josuke! There's a Stand user nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, there sure is. You and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Anyway, you see any vending machines around here? \NI'm dying of thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.00,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this? These aren't footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.59,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hands? Hand prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.89,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.64,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Josuke, the Stand just laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.39,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,See? Right here! On the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.19,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm letting this guy see my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.36,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's off his freakin' rocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.15,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's on the concrete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.65,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Where did it go? Where is it? It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.99,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Where did it go? It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:59.41,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Great... This guy is seriously bad news...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.46,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hermit Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Get out of here, you mutt! Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.90,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You hear that crying sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's coming from right here, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.24,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,A baby! I'm holding a naked baby in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.28,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I can tell now that I'm touching it. It's invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.66,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I-I can feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can really feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It's all squishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It's an invisible baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.76,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It feels like it's only about six months old or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But how did a baby turn invisible out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm assuming it's a Stand ability, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:13.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Why would an enemy Stand user turn a baby invisible, and where the hell did its mother go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:20.70,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Josuke, I think the baby actually {\i1}is{\i0} the Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It doesn't realize it's a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:28.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Since it became separated from its mother, \Nit instinctively turned invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:29.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:39.60,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Even adults can develop ulcers, bald spots, and gray hair \Nbefore they realize it for psychological reasons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.47,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I believe finding its mother is the only way to solve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hurry up and make it stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really sure what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:54.82,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I was in a situation similar to this before, but that was such a long time ago....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.11,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.62,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Did you figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.87,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Yes, when I touched it just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.42,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's a little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:14.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you can tell if it's a boy or girl\N by what's between their legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Figure something else out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.05,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.52,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...do you have any tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Th-That smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I-Is it on your hand? A big one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:38.99,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-It's invisible, so I couldn't tell for sure until I smelled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.37,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And I just scratched my beard with this hand!
Comment: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.17,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Here's your manuscript back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:01.18,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,I eagerly await the fixes for the volume release, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:08.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,For the time being, we're gonna have to get milk and diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,And since she's naked, we need to get her some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.65,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What? I-I'm buying them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Of course. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It's too embarrassing for me to buy baby stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:32.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Rumors would start flying around about a sixteen-year-old delinquent who got some chick knocked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:37.59,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But I only have American traveler's checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can use my credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.97,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't buy anything too expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:50.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I worked hard to build up my savings, and I don't have a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.65,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.56,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.19,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.28,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Umm... Do you carry disposable diapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.41,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Of course! Is this your first visit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Why, yes it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:12.58,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,These diapers are easy to change, \Neven if you're living on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.17,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,They even work overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:20.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Umm... I need diapers for a baby, not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:25.01,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,M-My apologies! So you're in need of baby diapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.18,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Do you need cloth diapers, or disposable pull-ups? {Omutsu type is "cloth diapers," pantsu type is "disposable pull-ups}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.27,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Uh... Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:37.02,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,As you can see, this one requires a diaper cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:40.44,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,...but disposable pull-ups like this are simple and economical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really sure which to get, so could you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.66,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Which size do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.41,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Size?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.49,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,How old is the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:59.59,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Depending on the baby's size, we have newborn, S-size, M-size, \NL-size, and XL-size for both boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Th-There are that many options nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:08.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,W-Well, she's a girl, and she felt about this big while I held her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.35,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "while I held her," sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:17.65,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,It would be very inconvenient for everyone if you bought\N the wrong size and tried to return them after they were soiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:22.11,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Oh, fine then! Give me every size.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.95,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I also need baby wipes, powdered milk, and a baby bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.12,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,For baby bottles, we have both glass and plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.12,Secondary,Joseph,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:35.37,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Glass ones don't scratch or start to smell as easily, but some babies may have trouble holding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.38,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Plastic ones are easier to hold, \Nbut may take on a noticeable scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.05,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Which do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:46.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,U-U-Uh... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.89,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Both variants come in many shapes and designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:51.85,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Some are even shaped like rocket ships and racing cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.10,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,The baby can hold this one by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.85,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,And if you turn this one upside-down, \Nthe tiny doll inside moves about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:03.48,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I-I'm not sure which to get, \Nso if you could just toss a few in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.74,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,And which bottle nipples would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.24,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,The rubber ones are soft, but don't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.08,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Silicon ones last, but they're a bit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.25,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,This is a vented nipple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:22.88,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,There's a diaphragm where the nipple goes in the mouth, \Nand the flow of milk is adjusted by how hard the baby sucks on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.84,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,This one is a German NUK nipple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:29.80,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,It has a slightly flattened shape, \Nwhich is said to more closely mimic the feel of a mother's breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:35.18,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,And much like while drinking breast milk, \Nthe milk won't come out unless the baby uses its jaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:39.98,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,O-Oh, all right. They're all fine! I'll take them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:44.23,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,And as for the nipple hole shapes,\N we have round, Y-shaped, and cross-shaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.36,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,J-Just give me all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.12,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And throw in some baby socks and clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm paying for all of this by card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.42,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:07.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,130,000... I'm not very familiar with yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.97,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,How much is that supposed to be in dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.47,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If one hundred yen is about eighty cents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.72,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Bah, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:20.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I need all of these things, and it's just baby stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Surely it can't be {\i1}that{\i0} expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What is he doing? He's taking forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.82,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.70,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the girl who got the ring? I wonder what happened with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.03,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,He never got an answer, so I'm curious if she said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.58,Main,Bitches,0,0,0,,Maybe she's just feeling conflicted about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.58,Secondary,Josuke,0,0,0,,I-I gotta get the hell away from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.96,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,If anyone from school saw me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.21,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.21,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Here's your card back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.13,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're done? A-All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We don't have to worry about losing her anymore, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:02.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...if anyone walks by and notices that \Nshe doesn't have a face, they'll freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.85,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,No need to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.73,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I picked up some makeup, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.40,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Let's put some foundation on her. Just a little bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, she actually looks kinda cute now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.83,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,My, what a darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Knowing what she looks like should help us find her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:29.13,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Finally a shred of hope! We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What a nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:35.72,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You really think so?\NAll right, now let's put on some lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:39.85,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Now for the eyebrows and eyelashes... Just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.14,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I knew he'd react that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.40,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's the kind of old guy who gets \Ncarried away by one simple compliment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.69,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Now we can carry you around \Nwithout having to worry about losing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.20,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We can't put makeup on your eyes, \Nso you'll just have to wear these sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,They look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Here, her milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.33,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Perhaps I went a bit light on the foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.13,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It looks as though it may be coming off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.46,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I-It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:15.26,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Sh-She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.85,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Sh-She disappeared! Along with my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The baby isn't just making herself invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,She's making everything around her invisible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar! Let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:32.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hurry up and let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,M-My hands are still invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.03,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,She's powering up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.05,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:02.01,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It looks like everything within \Nthirty centimeters of her is turning invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But this makes no sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:11.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If she's constantly protecting herself with her Stand, \Nwho was able to feed and take care of her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.90,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,She must be doing this because she feels anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.90,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.99,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be touched by any strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:23.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If she powers up any more, \Nnobody will be able to get close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.62,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We'll end up invisible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.17,Thoughts,Dude,0,0,0,,What a weird piece of crap. \NWho's gonna clean that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.13,Thoughts,Dude,0,0,0,,Guess someone will get to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.59,Thoughts,Dude,0,0,0,,Sure ain't gonna be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.55,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.64,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.98,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The lit cigarette butt... Oh, you can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing, Mr. Joestar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can't space out at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.57,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The stroller completely disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.17,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,She really is stressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The more scared she is, the bigger her range becomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.68,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,That sounds like the stroller flipped over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The baby... fell into the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.61,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is she? Make some noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't even see any bubbles! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.78,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,J-Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.58,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,This wouldn't have happened if he had just kept it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.62,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Stupid old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.29,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,How can my dad be such an irresponsible guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.79,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,He was irresponsible enough to\N abandon my mom for sixteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.46,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I could never respect someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.51,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,We'll never get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.64,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Stay the hell out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.10,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Where is she? She should be right around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.81,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't care if I turn invisible, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.69,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Just touch me already! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.90,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.95,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,She's not here... Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:29.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dammit! How the hell am I supposed to \Nfind an invisible baby in clear water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.37,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Josuke, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:43.55,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I may die in the next few moments, \Nso if I do, give your mother my regards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.01,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:50.18,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm quite old now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:21:00.07,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm adding color to the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,She's in the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:11.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The color of the blood is turning invisible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You'll find her in the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.35,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Nobody else would have even \Nconsidered doing something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Especially not for someone else's kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Nobody would go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I just wanted to look cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.32,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...in front of you.
Comment: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Well, a lot happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:08.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but it looks like everything's good for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.60,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,130,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:20.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,M-My hard-earned savings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:23.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That stupid geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:23.86,Secondary,Joseph,0,0,0,,There, there.
